%sql
select FIRST(artist) AS ArtistName, FROM_UNIXTIME(FIRST(ts)/1000.0) AS Timestamp, FIRST(firstName) AS FirstName , FIRST(lastName) AS LastName
from df1 INNER JOIN df2 ON df1.user_id=df2.userid 
INNER JOIN df3 ON df1.id=df3.id 
GROUP BY artist ORDER BY COUNT(artist) desc LIMIT 10
